sequenceDiagram
  participant U as User
  participant FE as Frontend
  participant GW as Nginx Gateway
  participant INS as Inspection Service
  participant EXT as Extinguisher Service
  participant USR as User Service
  participant ADM as Admin

  U->>FE: Schedule inspection
  FE->>GW: POST /api/inspections
  GW->>INS: Create inspection PENDING
  INS->>EXT: Verify extinguisher exists
  EXT-->>INS: OK
  INS-->>FE: Inspection created

  ADM->>FE: Assign inspector
  FE->>GW: PATCH /api/inspections/:id/assign
  GW->>INS: Assign inspector
  INS->>USR: Verify inspector role
  USR-->>INS: exists
  INS-->>FE: Status SCHEDULED

  participant INSP as Inspector
  INSP->>FE: Complete inspection
  FE->>GW: PATCH /api/inspections/:id/complete
  GW->>INS: Mark COMPLETED
  INS-->>FE: Done

  INSP->>FE: Log maintenance
  FE->>GW: POST /api/maintenance
  Note over GW: maintenance-service
  GW->>INS: Validate inspection COMPLETED
  INS-->>GW: OK
  GW->>EXT: Update extinguisher status
  EXT-->>FE: Maintenance recorded
